messages.content: *She understands that this guard could definitely arrest her, and that she presumably isn't being summoned for anything good, although this doesn't quite strike her as the way a wanted fugitive would be addressed, so maybe she needs to serve as a witness again... say, to what Intuition Overdrive did?* "Where to?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Does it matter? It's a secure location. I doubt you've heard of it."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *A prison?* "It does matter."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I see. It would be the Quercus Exchange Site. A building famously used for negotiations as well as hostage situations."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *Uh... Quercus Alba?* "Is a man named 'Intuition Overdrive' involved in this?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She was most likely asked for by said Intuition Overdrive, who most likely wants to kill her.* "Lead the way."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
It is the end of another night by the time they reach a door in the middle of nowhere, leading underground.

"I'm only supposed to accompany you this far. No runnin' off, okay? I'm head of Arenda guard, I'd have the authorization to kill you."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She is slightly concerned for her life, but that isn't particularly important. She could be fine if she just dies here in Arctica...? She would only need to stall until she snaps back to reality, at least, and then her body here would hopefully be separated enough for her not to die if someone stabs her, maybe, if she's lucky, although she has remained here for a relatively lengthy period of time already.* "Should I enter?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yes. There's only one path up until where you'll meet with 'im."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She dismounts her ghost horse, pulls the door open, steps inside, and shuts it behind her.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "My job done. I'm gonna go get wasted, awww yeah." The man can be heard saying this outside.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: The door leads to STAIRS.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She takes a few deep breaths, notches a crossbow bolt and, crossbow-in-hand, steps down the stairs.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
The stairs lead to a hallway, and the hallway eventually leads to a room with a single table and chairs on either side.

Seated at the end opposite where Rikarasu entered is someone fully covered in armor, with a mask that looks like a face like if someone made a mold of someone's face and then made it out of metal. Across the torso is a variety of standout threads of fabric tied around the body in such a way that it resembles the shape :wyrdwyrd:.

"Sit." He says, voice distorted.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

inlineEmojis.name: wyrdwyrd
inlineEmojis.imageUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\966890007677780048-1693B.png

messages.content: *She looks at him inscrutably and sits on the free chair.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are you 'Intuition Overdrive'?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: A deep breath can be heard. "No. Not remotely. You have clearly been ill-informed. I am Wyrd." This explains everything.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That is an unusual name. I presume it to be a pseudonym."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Do you intend to kill me, 'Wyrd'?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: ((wyrd is the word))

author.name: legoskelton
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\7324d6b2e5e7b2d85c445c799b852d80-F5E1E.png

messages.content: ((wired))

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: ((Wyrd))

author.name: zzazz
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\00e5cb55aacbe3824e8b8a9d53aac811-1CCD0.png

messages.content: "Not if you do not give me cause to. You have saved me the trouble of getting you to confirm you are aware of Intuition Overdrive, at least."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I have no intent of concealing the truth."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are you attempting to solve a particular mystery?'

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Something akin to that. Intuition Overdrive is a criminal. There is no question about that. But traditional methodology of justice cannot touch him."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "So you act as a vigilante?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: Wyrd pauses at this question for a bit. "...Yes. In a sense."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I do not intend to kill 'Intuition Overdrive'. I know him as an intruder and a fugitive, but scarcely as a murderer, let alone an outright liar."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "You may cut to the chase. What did you summon me for?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"A plea bargain. I have channels of connection to government authority. Your suspicion in ongoing cases will be resolved, and you will be provided with full citizenship as well as the means to reside here comfortably until such a point as you are able to return wherever it is you hail from. All I ask is your cooperation in the detainment of the Groverfield heir."

Wyrd shakes his head. 
"He will not be killed. Though traditional channels are, again, non-viable, I have arranged for an informal trial. I am aware he has extenuating circumstances in the state of his existence, but he cannot continue to run rampant. You may bear witness to this trial if it clears doubts of impartiality."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She pauses. The offer seems almost too convenient, even considering that he calls himself 'Wyrd'.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Do you know where 'Intuition Overdrive' is at this moment?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I can approximate his location, but I am not entirely certain. At any rate, I have a plan to bring him into view."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Elaborate."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"I am intimately familiar with his mother." An airhorn sounds at this sick burn, but only metaphorically. "With this connection and his fixation on playing detective, it should be trivial to pique his curiosity. I cannot act myself, nor do I believe Katrielle will knowingly act against her son's interest. But with the situation properly set up, you should be able to easily force him into a corner."

Wyrd clears his throat. "I will only provide further details if you agree to assist."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She sees no real reason to pass this up, at least provided nothing prevents her from backing out yet.* "I will."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Very well." Wyrd then begins to explain more details, as such, and thusly. And Rikarasu listens to them.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((end chapter 5 and session))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Wyrd continues. "Are you familiar with *The Antarctica Project*?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...I have heard the name."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "The specifics are irrelevant. What matters is that Intuition Overdrive will not be on this world for a period of time. And also that I have suspicions you are also connected to this other world."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Are you referring to the world containing the planet known as Earth?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yes."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That is where I reside."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Do you want me to find him there?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "That should not be necessary. Though I suppose knowing where to find him when he is there could end up as a useful asset if things go unexpectedly."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Ah."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Earth is split into about two-hundred countries, which are part of several large landmasses known as continents, largely separated by sea. I do not know what country Intuition Overdrive has been transported to, but it is likely to be far from the one I reside in, so physically locating him would be difficult."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Regardless, if you do not intend for me to find him there, what do you need my assistance for?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "You can communicate with him, right?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She hesitates.* "...Sometimes."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I possess a device that allows me to communicate with two groups. One group comprises of those who came from Earth, and one comprises of every 'participant', whether they came from Earth or Arctica. 'Intuition Overdrive' is only part of the latter group, which can only be used when every participant is in the same location, either Earth or Arctica."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Someone evidently left Arctica recently, as the connection was severed... just a minute ago."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I see. I'm not aware of the schedule this runs by."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She sends out some messsages and thinks back.* "I do possess some information regarding that of plausible veracity."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Several hours ago, I was told that our transfers were all synchronised. The Arcticans would transfer on the morning after the next day, a Saturday, and we would return to Earth on Monday."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "In other words, you may presume that I will only return to Earth in two days' time."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "That matches up, I suppose."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She takes out her map and tries to locate Montana.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: Montana is one of the provinces of Arctica. It's to the east.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What do you wish for me to say to him when I am able to?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I may be able to extract his location from him with some questioning, but he could now be more cautious."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She puts the map away.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I know where he is right now. But it's true that with his resources, he could quickly make his way anywhere nigh undetected. The idea is instead to eliminate this ambiguity by forcing him to head towards one specific location."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I see."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "And where is that "one specific location"?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "It could be in various places. But the ideal one is, in fact, right here. In this very complex."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Is there something else magically or architecturally special about this 'complex', or is it simply convenient for providing a small, closed-in area?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "It is mostly the latter, but I've made other preparations. Even if he brought someone with the ability to teleport for some reason, that person would be unable to within this area."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She nods.* "Is that the entirety of your plan? I lure him to come to this area, then you capture him and put him on trial?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “In summary, yes.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Is there any further detail you wish for me to know now?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “If you desire to know more, perhaps. But that is the extent of what is strictly necessary to inform you of. On the other end, I wish to know when next you and Intuition will both be here. Please leave a note or something at this location if you discover this information and I am not around.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...I am satisfied with what I know at this point, and I will do as you request."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "On that note, however, is there any way I could access teleportation, or another faster method of transportation? It would be more convenient if I was able to return here quickly when necessary, and I would ideally like to visit a location in the province of Montana as soon as possible."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Of course, I understand that teleportation should be impossible within this area, but it would presumably be possible to teleport close outside the bubble in which that applies."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I am capable of teleporting people. You may also utilize public transit.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What varieties of public transit exist here?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Teleportation.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Oh."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She pauses with uncertainty again, and realises she needs to get her own story straight. Three things. One: She needs to confront Haruka Tanaka here. It makes no sense for Fainda not to, and even if it did, any concerns over loss of cases or income are fairly irrelevant to her now. Two: She needs to have a specific claim to confront Haruka with. She can easily say that the Tanaka family is conspiring against her somehow, and maybe even responsible for the Arctican abduction, but how can she explain the cases 'given under false pretenses' in the first place? She claimed earlier that Ryuki was with the police, and wanted her clientless and estranged, so what could she then claim Haruka knew there? Maybe... Haruka... wanted the truth to be buried, and forced Ryuki to try to get her justifiably fired? Maybe she stole the real music box? She'll figure it out. Three: She needs to stick to the 'time travel' mystery, and she's claimed they're still in Arctica, so she needs to stick to that. As she did in Arctica, she's essentially conducting investigation on two levels — the fact that nothing Haruka said about the existing mystery on Earth would necessarily have any meaning if this wasn't the real Earth or the real Haruka is being ignored.*

She can hash out any details in argument, as implied, and she's supposed to be at Haruka's house in the hour.* "Thank you. I will not be doing that, as there is nothing to clarify."

messages.content: Haruka answers. She stares at Alicia. “Who is this?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Alicia Matel. She is accompanying me."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Is there a problem?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yes. I don't know this girl. I don't want her entering my home."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Alicia mutters indistinctly.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Alicia Matel is an acquaintance of mine. I wish for you to allow me to enter with her, and I assure you that she will do no harm."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Why? She has no relevance to me."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "She has relevance to me."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "And for my own safety, I want to be accompanied."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Your own *safety*?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Do you not understand the value of a bodyguard?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I'm not a young woman anymore. You're the one who'd be able to physically overpower me, were it to come to that. And I doubt this girl would change much."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I could be ambushed. Others live in this house."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
She stares at you.

"...Okay. Fine. This isn't worth fighting over. She may enter, for now. Welcome, Matel." She rudely forgoes the honorific on PURPOSE. 
"Come in."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She enters.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She takes a seat.* "What did you want to meet here for?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“I was wondering where you’ve been, for one.”

Yasu is sitting at the table, staring at a notebook. Haruka walks up to him. “Ichigo, I’m working. Do this elsewhere.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Ah, Yasuyasu." *She turns to look at him.* "Do you know Ms. Erica Furuda?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Who?”

Haruka sighs. “You aren’t related to this. I don’t even want you following her around anymore.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I was missing because I was in Arctica, which has the appearance of being on another planet. I was not available on Earth during that time."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Does that explanation make sense to you?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She's oversimplifying, of course.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Not in the slightest, no. Ichigo, *leave*.” She gets stern.

“Just one minute.” He responds quietly, flipping through papers.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Have the two of you fell out?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Our relationship is *fine*. It is not your business, and I would like to apologize for his inconveniencing you while stressing that I do not want you dragging him along on things again.”

The boy puts his hand on his forehead in exasperation. Alicia sits awkwardly.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She narrows her eyes at Haruka.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Is who he 'chooses to associate with in his own time' your business?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Yes, I would very well think so. I’m not one of those latchkey mothers.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Perhaps I have failed to make myself clear to this point. The truth is my business. It is what I live for, and to uncover it is my duty."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Mhm, good.” Haruka pulls a paper out from the collection of papers IchigoYasu is looking through and examines it.

“What exactly is this… meeting about…?” Alicia is baffled.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She shakes her head.* "...And don't think I haven't caught onto your scheme, Haruka Tanaka."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "You are conspiring against me. I know this to be fact. Are you willing to repent and admit your sins now, or will I need to explain them for us all to hear?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Shut up.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: Haruka slaps Ichigo in the face. Ichigo stumbles over from the impact, knocking his chair over with him.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
“Whoa, what?!” Alicia is surprised.

“I can’t deal with both of these things at once. You’re all forcing me into a very difficult spot.” Haruka speaks with an unwavering certainty.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She looks at Alicia.* "Listen closely, Alicia Matel. I shall explain the truth now, once, and for all."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Is this really the—“ Alicia looks between everyone.

“This charlatan was GONE. You were free from distractions. How are you still failing?!” Haruka screams at Ichigo, who stammers over his words.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
She hits him again, and Alicia gets up. “That’s enough, woman!”

Haruka sneers at her. “Oh, get over yourself. You’re going to claim a moral high ground here? You don’t even know me.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “It’s not like I’ve even done anything. He’s overreacting with the presence of an audience. Everyone always trying to take advantage of me. It’s sickening.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She sighs, puts away her weapon, pulls out her pocketbook, opens up a random blank page, and quickly sketches out a chart, which looks like this but handwritten and using kanji and katakana. I don't know why this needed a chart either.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

attachments.url: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\accuratefamilytree-1CC1B.png

messages.content: *She rips out the page at its edges, puts down the pocketbook, and gets up, her voice somewhat stronger.* "Allow me, as a start, to *explain* the matter of the relationship between son and mother you see here. She may be playing up her attitude, considering that neither of us are impressed and this scene could have been saved for any other moment, but it is clear that their "fine" relationship is struggling." *She holds up the chart.* "Ichigo Culbasko is the illegitimate child of Zaquero Culbasko. Haruka Tanaka did not want me to know his name. He used a fake name, Yasuyasu Miyamoto and, in fact, I only learned that he was her son when her hand was forced to tell me. I once heard her refer to her son as Ichigo Culbasko, but I had no reason to assume Miyamoto and Culbasko were related. It is evident that there is a reason they have fallen out as you see, and a reason for this conflict over paperwork. That reason is what he learned. A few weeks or months ago, possibly four or three months ago, Ichigo Culbasko learned that he was an illegitimate child. As a 'bastard son', he clearly grew to resent his mother, leading to this strained relationship, which caused her to force him out of his role in the conspiracy. As for the papers, they are his punishment, an attempt to 'set him on the right path'. To be specific, Ichigo Culbasko is being forced to write lines — to copy sentences hundreds or thousands of times. You recall Haruka Tanaka inspecting their quality, and exclaiming the phrase "this charlatan was GONE." That was one of the lines that he was instructed to write, and he has clearly struggled at it, causing the reaction from Haruka Tanaka you see here."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "That is the truth of this... case."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
Haruka is not dissuaded from abusing her child by this.

“This clearly isn’t the time, jackass.” Alicia steps in and pushes Haruka against the wall.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She draws her weapon and points it vaguely in the direction of the two.* "Drop the issue."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
Haruka lets out a forced fake laugh. “Well, you’ve one thing right. Ichigo Culbasko. That’s my sons name. Ichigo means first son, and that’s true. That’s what he is. But why wouldn’t I have him take my surname?! Because it’s a message.”

Alicia stares at you, rolling her eyes, and backs off, still keeping her guard up.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “That I won’t just forget what that man’s done. His shitty biological father. You’re more of a god damn parent to him, Endo, and I don’t compliment you lightly.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “The rest is nonsense, of course. Ridiculous conclusions that vaguely connect to the facts. But it doesn’t matter. You were never supposed to be *good* at your job.” The normally very stone faced Haruka is incredibly expressive right now.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Unfortunate."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "So you saw Ichigo Culabsko's father in such a bad light that you chose to make his name serve as a reminder of his misdeeds? I fail to wonder how you ever could have conflicted."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “But he— Ichigo is supposed to be good. I’m not just some cruel monster, you know!! He needs to succeed in this pivotal period of his life. He’ll get a scholarship, a job — a good job — and he’ll live a life better than I ever could, and give his wife a proper relationship. I’m setting him up for a wonderful life. This here is a blip on the timeline.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...He has a wife? He is in high school."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “God, you really are a basket case, huh?” Alicia sighs. “I thought it was an eccentric character you put on.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
“Future tense. Obviously.” Haruka mutters.

We’re going to pretend this misunderstanding and clarification was possible and made sense in the original Japanese.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She glares at Alicia.* "Is 'needing to succeed' why you chose to involve him in your schemes, and why you physically attacked him for error in work moments after inspecting some as fine?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I am saner than anyone else in this room, and I am confident in that assessment."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “While we’re asking annoying clarifications, who the hell is Erica Furuda? I can certainly tell you that I wouldn’t make… this particular mistake more than one time. Referring to my own actions, of course.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Haruka says that.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Erica Furuda is Ichigo Culbasko's sister. She is the illegitimate Brazilian daughter of Zaquera Culbasko."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I have met her."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
Haruka scoffs. “Oh, certainly. I’m sure Zaquera’s left tons of people like me behind in his wake. But that has nothing to do with me.”
Ichigo stands back up. “I’m trying, Mom. Really, it’s just, a lot…”
Haruka growls. “I was in the process of getting over it before you gave that absurd excuse. Does your ‘trying’ necessitate coming home late nearly every day? Don’t *try to lie to me.*”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: Alicia whispers to you. “Thanks a lot for bringing me to this, pal.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It was no trouble."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She puts the ripped paper down on top of her pocketbook and pulls out her PDA.* "Do you have a boyfriend, Ichigo?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“What?” Ichigo stares.

“My son is not one of your ilk, Endo.” Haruka says with less disdain than the phrasing would imply but still inherently pretty rude.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "How can you possibly claim to know that, Haruka?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “He’s had endearing little crushes on the girls in his class he let me in on, back when we were on better terms. He is not a homosexual. I know my own son.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It is not unheard of for a person to be attracted to more than one gender simultaneously."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Oh, lord.” Haruka facepalms. “I don’t care about arguing this.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Then let Ichigo argue for himself."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I don’t— I’m not seeing anyone right now.” Ichigo is uncomfortable!

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Calm down. Your denials will be fruitless if you cannot support their veracity."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“We are not turning this meeting into an inquisition on my son’s sexuality.” Haruka pounds her hand on the table.

“Yeah…” Ichigo mutters.

“It’s incredible that even has to be specified.” Alicia shakes her head.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That is not my point. You are still angry at him."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What do you believe he could be "coming home late nearly every day" because of? Attending the funerals of people he murdered?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“I don’t care. Hanging out with his good for nothing friends, I assume.”

“Yeah!” Ichigo affirms. “I mean, no, they’re not good-for…”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I see. If you do not care, how do you ever expect to address the issue?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I don’t care about the specific form the issue takes.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Because you don't care about his feelings?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I care about my son’s feelings more than anyone! I’m just not prioritizing the ones he has moment to moment over his whole life.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Prove it."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “What the fuck does that mean? How can I ‘prove’ a matter of the heart? You’re tasked with proving far more substantial things and can’t even manage that!”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What "far more substantial things" do you refer to?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I’ve kept track, you know. Do you know how few cases you’ve actually *solved*? I even try to account for that, and make the resolutions asinine, and you still find a new way to go off the rails.” She smirks, looking over to Alicia. “I finally remember you. Alicia Matel, hm? I couldn’t recall the name. It’s good to know I can be open with everyone here. Hah.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She snorts.* "If you say so. Tell me, then, Haruka. How many of those cases ended with the truth having been uncovered?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Zero. In effect. Some were real problems you helped out with, I suppose. But saving a cat from a tree or whatever, that can hardly be called being a detective.”

Haruka shrugs. “I’m not saying this to be cruel, Rikarasu. Quite the opposite. I want you to know I’ve been acting purely in your interest up to now.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She feels slightly wounded, despite everything.* "..."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "...How so?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “You know, Zaquera, he made everyone else answer for his problems. Even when we were both young—but at any rate, I, I’m not like that. I was content to let you live life free from my own woes. You get an exorbitant salary for comparatively little work. With careful investment, you can be set for life by the time our arrangement is finished. And no damage to your psyche outside of me acting a little strange, that was the plan.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "So you claim you chose to do this specifically for me because of... what, exactly? Am I your illegitimate daughter? Is my blood of special significance to scientists?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Hmph. It didn’t *have* to be you, no. You were just in the right place and the right stage of life at the right time.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "And your son, on the other hand, was different? He deserved no 'life free from your own woes'?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “My son *does* live life free from my woes. I think he might have realized, but he has no relation to them whatsoever nor does he need to. That’s why I make sure he succeeds. So he doesn’t have to fall into the same hole as me.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: She shakes her head. “After all this time, I’m not going to expect you to specifically intuit what I’m talking about. Follow me, Ms. Endo. You two can do whatever.” Haruka heads down some stairs.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She's starting to think her comment about sanity was at least one-third true.*

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: ((hajime watching nagito abuse a child: There’s something wrong with him…))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((Exactly))

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She looks at Ichigo.* "I am certain you have not been paid an exorbitant salary."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I’m jobless.” He shrugs.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She neatly folds and pockets the 'chart', grabs and pockets her pocketbook, sends a text, and slowly goes after Haruka down the stairs.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“I suppose I’m too hard on you.” Haruka says reluctantly as she hears your approach.
“I mean, as indirect as your solutions may be, it’s something you thought would work. And I have no right to speak there. I hired you because I had the most ridiculous, obscenely convoluted idea for how to solve a problem.”

Haruka opens a door at the bottom of the stairs.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Your 'plan' is an affront to reality at its core. There is no possible problem greater than that."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She looks through the door.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “You can never just straightforwardly call someone a scumbag, can you?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "*Sinner.*"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
The organizational system makes it complicated, but this is a room full of stacks of banknotes and a smaller but still substantial amount of Foreign White Substance.

“Money laundering. That’s your career.” Haruka stares at you, less disdainful or annoyed or positive or negative, and mostly just tired.

((end session))

messages.content: *She stares at Haruka, not exactly sure how to respond. This isn't an impossible answer, but it's the kind of claim she'd expect to come up with. That's clearly a drug. Right?*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Is that fingerprint powder?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "It's cocaine. I should probably burn the stuff, since I obviously have enough pure cash. I guess it's... just in case."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Okay. Give me one reason not to call the police right now."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Because they'd lock you up. I'm not revealing this to you because I *trust* you, Endo. I'm revealing this to you because you're culpable."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I am an *unwitting* accomplice. How could I possibly be culpable?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: Haruka scoffs. "Endo, your existence isn't something that can hold up in court. Honestly, I myself assumed you'd intuited it at some point. A private investigator isn't a *real* job. It's a storytelling device that shares its name with a type of freeloader in real life. Nobody in this line of work makes as much money as you do."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "And I suppose you intend to claim that "storytelling device" simply came into existence out of nothing, Haruka? And that all I've done would be deemed so 'fundamentally different' from the investigations any private investigator you'd find in a phone book would undertake that my job would be deemed fake?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yes."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Let's pretend, for a foolish moment, that I believe you. Kamala Kyros has already been searching for me for months, and it is not unlikely that I would be arrested if any police officer who could recognise my face caught a glance at me. I am a wanted fugitive. Give me one reason not to murder you right now."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: She laughs. "You've always had a taste for the dramatic, huh? Truly, I cannot think of a single reason. You'd off me, and then one of the two people in this building would restrain you, and your life would be over. 'Two birds one stone', right?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "How could you possibly know that they would restrain me? They would be more likely to be understanding once they learned the scope of your deception."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "You certainly have no reason to claim to judge Alicia's character. We could easily hold a vote, here, in minutes."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "And what exactly do you think you know about Alicia? Do you know enough about her to believe in her? What about my *son*, huh? How confident are you that he would judge you as justified for killing me? Go ahead, *Fainda*. Call everyone over. This is what you live for, right? Gathering everyone to explain who the culprit is."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Naturally."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She yells upstairs.* "Come down here, everyone."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: Alicia comes down first. "What's up?" She looks around at the room.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Haruka Tanaka is a drug dealer, and she has confessed. I have been strung around as an unknowing accessory to money laundering."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What would you do if I killed her?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"Ichigo! Come down, please!" Haruka yells up the stairs.

Alicia's eyes widen. "Hm. So it's her, then? Wild. I dunno, I might kill you? It depends on the context. You mean like, if you did it right now?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Precisely."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I would be justified. She is a sinner of the highest order."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "With what, though? Your bare hands?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She brandishes her weapon.* "I have a gun. Did you not notice?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I see. In that case, I wouldn't do anything to you. I'd probably lose if we came in conflict." She looks over at Haruka. "So what specifically is your problem with her? Is it the drugs?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "*She is a sinner of the highest order.* She has conspired against me for years, and she undoubtedly intends to force me to willfully lie for our own safety."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"Alright, I guess." Alicia looks unenthused.

"Oh, for the love of god, quit roleplaying. You're not some superhero of justice. I'd have taken your objections to me more to heart if you didn't phrase them as childishly as you do everything." Haruka snaps at Rikarasu.

Ichigo 'Yasu' Culbasko comes down. "What's up?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Haruka Tanaka is a drug dealer, and she has confessed. I have been strung around as an unknowing accessory to money laundering."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What would you do if I killed her?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What?!" He attempts to tackle Rikarasu to the ground. ((grapple contest!!))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: You are pinned to the ground.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Agh!"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Think rationally, Yasu. People could have died because of her actions."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I never killed anyone. You've got a lot of nerve whining about my 'sins' and then lying to everyone you call down here." Haruka points at you.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I didn't claim you, personally, have committed murder. But drugs kill."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"You want me to think *rationally*? You just threatened to kill someone!" Yasu shakes his head. 
"I...I liked you, y'know. Mom only asked me to watch you twice. I stayed along with you on cases because it was interesting. I didn't want to admit it, and normally I'd never have told you. But you--you're sick! None of it was a persona, was it?! You think you can just do whatever you want? Because you appointed yourself an arbiter of the truth??? I mean, what else are you gonna use to justify it? The only other person who recognized your authority is the one you're trying to murder!" He's tearing up.

((This moment does not function because Yasu has not been in the story.))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "The truth matters above all else. I am not acting as any 'arbiter' here,  merely an executor — Haruka Tanaka has confessed, and you can see the evidence of her wrongdoing for yourself. You're only choosing to cling to your own arbitrary idea of 'authority'. As if the government have greater moral quality simply because more people recognise their authority? If you think that way, your ideals are shallow, Ichigo." *She tries to push Yasu off.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
Yasu is pushed off.
"Shut the fuck up, Endo. And don't you dare touch him."
Haruka walks right up into Rikarasu's face and speaks softly.
"Do you think anyone's buying this? Maybe you're deluded enough to buy it yourself, but I can guarantee no one else is."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She stands to face her.* "I would rather die than play along with your schemes, Haruka Tanaka."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"I've been nothing but kind. My original plan would have left you untraceable. I only made your involvement an issue when you betrayed me yourself. You think I've been *conspiring against you*? Give me a break. I am the only person who has ever done anything for you, you ungrateful wretch."

Alicia mutters. "I mean, if you don't find the government's laws inherently more meaningful, I don't think you can say it matters that she's been committing crimes."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It *matters* that she has been willfully deceiving the police, and will continue to do so."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Oh, deceit this, truth that! Unbelievable. Endo, I want to ask you something. When's the last time you've been honest about *anything*?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Moments ago."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "At its core, the truth is what allows the world to function. Society sets punishments for acts that society deems undesirable, and so it creates forces with the aim of discovering those culpable for those acts. Those punishments do not override the prerogative individuals have not to begrime the truth, and at the same time, nor does fear of them. Any trust from the general populace in the legal system is based around its ability to effectively discover the truth."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I've never lied to a police officer. Not once. And I certainly won't have the chance to if you kill me. So your smarmy technical answer doesn't even work."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "This is not a 'smarmy technical' answer. You are fully aware that you are a wanted criminal. Are you willing to turn yourself in?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"Oh, and now you care about the law!" She cackles. "No. I'm not done yet. I won't stop until I've seen this through, until my family is set. If you're so dedicated to ruining your own life, go ahead, Endo. Or maybe you don't trust the law, and you kill all three people here yourself? Live a long happy life, with stains that will never wash off! I wonder what kind of work you'll be able to find when your references are all six feet under?"

Her visage turns grim. It's closer to the unexpressive Haruka Tanaka you're used to. 
"Ever since I was young, I performed thorough background checks on everyone I ever worked with. Even when Zaquera was too lazy to do it, I made sure to. And I've kept up that habit to this very day."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Good for you."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Do you believe I have no plan? I have one convenient, guaranteed way out of any situation I could possibly catch myself in, and more than one convenient, less guaranteed way out of any such situation. You have no idea what the scope of the 'scenario' this meeting has occurred in is, Haruka Tanaka."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Money laundering is committed with the goal of *concealing the source of income*. No technicalities you attempt to use will change your clear moral position here. You are manipulative, you are obsessive, and you are a sinner."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"Please, stop fighting! This is bound to end badly..." Yasu.

Haruka pays him no mind. "What, that project or whatever?" She rolls her eyes. "I mentioned the background checks for a reason, you know. I just want to see the master detective in action, dedicated to the truth above all else. Hell, I'll turn myself in if you can answer this one!"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "More than that."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What do you expect me to expose now? Some 'dark secret' about myself you've been able to uncover? That my real name is Rikarasu Endo? That I'm actually a violent sociopath with the goal of destroying all of humanity?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are you a man or a woman, Rikarasu Endo? That's all. A parting gift for our partnership."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "A woman."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Threatening to murder me, for one. If I'm clever enough, I can probably get you for possession of illegal materials. You seem to think you're in a position to make demands of others, Endo. That is a flagrant contradiction with the truth."
