messages.content:
~~((End session))~~

She catches a bit of rest. She is woken up by the entrance of a new person into this holding area. A woman who looks like she’s American, or maybe some sort of Hispanic, or maybe the embodiment of exhaustion.

She walks up to your cell. “Rikarasu Endo?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Rikarasu Endo? What? Who's that?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “You, smartass. Please don’t make this harder than it has to be. I know everything. And I’m your ticket out of here.” She turns to Hirer Dreng. “I don’t even know why the hell you’re here, but you’re coming with me too.” Hirer smirks in a way that conveys no information.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Who are you?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “God, no. Look, I’m the only person who gives a shit anymore, apparently, even though I was the one opposing this whole thing. Call me Soul. I’m your ‘Attorney’. This kind of detainment is obviously not kosher, and I’m quite good at whistleblowing. Dismissing charges will be a slightly more involved process, but nobody will be able to stop us from leaving.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Soul... What do you mean "obviously not kosher"? Are you familiar with Japanese law?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Enough of it anyway.” She’s speaking to you in Japanese, but not very good Japanese. She did switch to obviously fluent English for Hirer.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Um... If we're leaving, can you find my pocketbook?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I could easily get it. Don’t know if it would be legal, but I could.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It was evil to take it in the first place, no?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Dunno, probably? I really don’t care, I’ll get it, fine.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Great."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "So?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“So that’s it. Gate’s already unlocked.” She opens it for you. Hirer springs out of his cell.

The third guy speaks up. “Y’know, I actually—“

“Shut up.” Soul does not care about him.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She gets up and steps out.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She looks back and forth across the hallway, trying to locate an exit with her newfound field of vision.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: Soul grabs Hirer by the arm, anticipating some devious escape attempt from him. She heads out the direction to the exit.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She follows.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
They leave the building uneventfully. Kamala doesn’t seem to be there.

Soul shoves Hirer into the back seat of a car. “Get in.” She requests of Rikarasu.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She gets in without showing much reluctance.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
It drives.

"You ever read the Bible, Endo?" Soul says this normal question.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I see. Yeah, I guess you'd..." She mutters. "There was someone else I wanted to talk to about this. You're my second choice. Ideally I wouldn't have to drag you off like this, but you'd ideally not want to be in jail, so I guess we're even."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I see." *She nods slowly.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "My ears are open."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What's the most common name in the world?"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I don't recall. Mark? Mohammed?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"It's the latter. I think it is. I mean, you could get technical, since there's quite a few different ways to spell it, and there's no comprehensive global census... but it's very easily the winner. It makes sense, anyway. Religion is important to a lot of people, and while only some Christians see it as normal to give your child the name of their prophet, it's much more common in Muslim communities. Add some conveniently high population densities, and it seemed like no other name would ever be able to catch up."
She parks the car to the side of some random street.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Of course, I suppose a number of the individuals with that name must be disgusted by their association with such a figure."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Okay, wow, we'll put a pin in that. Anyway..." She hands a printed out spreadsheet to Rikarasu. "This is 2022 global estimate data from the US Census Bureau. Mohammad is *eighth*."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...That is natural, isn't it? The name is so common that a huge amount of people in America were given it, but most people named Mohammad would still live in African and Asian countries."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
The spreadsheet lists the seven names more common than Mohammad.
Eric, Erika, Bruce, Alex, Alicia, Bruno, and Alexa. 'Erica' is counted as a variation of Erika, much like all the different spellings for Mo/uhamma/ed.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Where the *fuck* are all these Erics? I could swear I had never met a *single* person named Eric." Soul seems insanely agitated about this.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You call yourself Soul."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "And? I'm not mocking the name. That's not the point."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "But Eric is a 'normal' name. I doubt you would care to associate with 'normal' people."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I work at a fuckin' highschool, man. I know what people are named. But sure, yeah. My anecdotal evidence isn't data. But it shook me. I double checked their sources. I have no intrinsic faith in these sorts of organizations. And every Eric in the data set was fully accounted for. It was real, accurate."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I... see." *She thinks.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "How many people with the other names on the list have you met? For example, Erika, Bruce, Alex, Alicia, Bruno, Alexa, and Mohammad."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I know one guy named Bruce. I've met a few guys named Alex, I think? Definitely exactly two Mohammad's, though I wouldn't be in the same place as the bulk of them. And I know *of* two people named Erika, if not personally. That's all I can think of offhand."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Have you seeked out an Eric? Perhaps questioning them and their parents would be the first step to reach the heart of the conspiracy."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"I did actually look into a few. It didn't reveal anything, which seems obvious when we talk about it like this. They were normal enough people, with actual histories. I was even able to get a few stories of why the name was chosen." She groans. 

"Before this, I also obviously checked earlier census data to compare and deal with this feeling of confusion. That was actually when I really lost it, because it's the same thing. These have *always* been the most popular group of names. A surge in people born named Eric? That's unusual, but trends happen. A sudden increase in records due to previously undocumented Erics? That's the stupidest thing I've ever heard, but would logically explain the discrepancy. But this was me being told outright that my memories were wrong. I asked my coworker about this, trying to weave it into conversation naturally. He mentioned that yeah, he was pretty sure Eric was the most popular. But then... I contacted a different sort of coworker. Someone I don't tend to speak to."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...And? Did they confirm that you were being gaslit?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yeah. They agreed with me. Muhammad. Actually, someone they used to work with is *named* Mohammad. I'd like to have them ask, but they're not exactly on speaking terms. It doesn't really matter. The point is-- you're the third guy. You're, if not proof, a pretty convincing argument in favor of what I'd hypothesized."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...I'm Japanese."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I don't really understand what that has to do with anything. I mean because you're part of The Antarctica Project."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I don't really understand what that has to do with anything."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
She makes an exasperated noise. "You're still on that level of understanding, I guess. I still kind of have to avoid spoiling things related to that, infuriatingly. But there's a lot of reasons to suspect a connection. I asked a bunch of people. Honestly, everyone at the school probably thinks I'm a lunatic at this point. Knows, I guess. None of them agreed with my memory of events. Nobody could understand anything I thought was odd. Most importantly, just..."
She curls her fingers into her hair, furious. "Jesus didn't have a fucking disciple named Eric! I would remember that! That's a major cultural work of literature!!!!!!!!!!!!" She finally makes eye contact with Rikarasu. "Someone is fucking with the *truth itself*, alright?! And that's not even the part that gets me, that someone has that kind of power. It's that they're using it for *this*. Why would anyone do this?????"

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "But the name must have *some* documented origin, mustn't it?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "A conspiracy on the level you describe would seem little short of controlling reality itself."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yes. Make of that what you will."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Just as you said."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: She sighs, somehow calmed by your words. "The documented origin doesn't really help. Eric's a name that traces back to Old Norse. It could maybe have been around in the first centuries CE, as something altered. Regardless, people -- in the copious academic texts that have *always existed* about the *famous biblical figure Eric* -- think whatever name he had is probably not contiguous with modern Erics. Just for geographic reasons."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "The name Erica, though, is just a feminine version of Eric. Do they not exist in relation to one another?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Yeah, Erica is related etymologically. There doesn't seem to be anything unusual there. I mean, it's absolutely unusual there's that many Ericas, but I don't think it would be for a different reason than whatever is happening with Eric. The two names are very blatantly linked."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "But you've met people named Erica. That's different."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Ehhhh. Not really. I've communicated with one indirectly, and the other I don't even know in any personal capacity. She was already dead by the time I first heard of her."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "That's besides the point, though. Even knowing a few wouldn't change the core of this. I do know a few people with those top list names."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What do you propose we do, then?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
"That's a really good question."

((End session))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Listen. I need to take you somewhere, alright? This is important."

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Where?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “My… god, it’s fucking embarrassing saying it like this out loud… my lab.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I am proud of you for saying it anyway."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "But where is your lab?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Back in America, unfortunately. We could take the long way, but I have a better method.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Tunnel?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “What? Like, across the entire ocean? Huh?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "If you dig down, you could reach America on the other end."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
She silently starts driving the car again. She doesn’t have a response to that.

Hirer Dreng, who is still here, speaks. “Uh, can you send me, like, anywhere else?”

Soul mutters a non-commital answer.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What do you have to do with yourself, Hirer Dreng?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Not sure how I got here. Something to do with Intuition Overdrive, I think. I just figured guys like us could team up, maybe get out of this mess. Seems we’ve been bailed, though. Great.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She shrugs.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Man, where even is this? Sorry, I lost track after the lady started talking about people named Eric.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Japan?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Ah, okay. …Yeah, I don’t know why I thought I’d get anything out of an answer to that. What kinda place is it?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "In what way?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I don’t know? How’s the food, the people, the government, is there a lot of crime, is it a shithole, I’m just trying to have a conversation.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "The food is good. The people are of varying quality. The government is... better than Arctica's. Their policing leaves something to be desired. There is certainly crime, but a relatively tolerable level. I would not call my country a shithole."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "What about yours? How are your country's foods, people, and government? Is it crime-ridden or a 'shithole'?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Food’s alright. People suck, governments whatever. Guess crime depends on the place. Kind of a shithole in my case, though.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Unsurprising."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "You live under a monarchy. I find that to be a poor system of government."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Yeah, well. Sucks, but nothing exists that’d suck much less.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What if I were to rule?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I mean, I don’t know. I still don’t really know who you are. Maybe it’d be better than the king we got, but that’d still just be a monarchy, right?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "A monarchy implies a line of succession. I believe that if I were to dictate over a country for a sufficient period of time, I could fix it such that no ruler would be necessary after myself."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I also do not plan to have children."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: He laughs. “What, you’re gonna teach us all to live among our fellow man going forward? Yeesh. Good choice on the children thing, though. Probably… not a good idea. For you.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What are you implying by that?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "As for my theoretical policies, I believe the root of all human conflict is lying. All that is ultimately necessary is to eradicate it."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Look, most parents? They think of having a kid as this huge responsibility. I get where they come from, yeah. They want to do everything right. But nobody can do that. Ever. Eventually… you’re gonna fuck up. Gonna lose your composure at the wrong time, gonna not be enough for their needs. You’ve got limitless influence over this dumb little gremlin and everything wrong with ‘em will be your fault. The only parent who can make it through, and not lose their fuckin’ mind, is one who goes in with the assumption that they’re evil and going to ruin the child. Then it’s all uphill from there. You’re too idealistic to have a kid. They’d be scared shitless of you, I’d bet all I own on it. Not to mention your husband. Yikes! Relationships are more or less the same deal, at that.”
Hirer finishes explaining his normal opinions.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “Hey, I’m gonna beat you up so badly you’ll never walk again.” He smirks, and does nothing.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “What are you two *fucking*…” Soul gives up on whatever interruption she was almost going to go with.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I'm not sure."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Do you truly consider me overly idealistic?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I feel that it would be unhealthy for someone to desire a better world less than I do."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Yeah, obviously you would. If you didn’t, you wouldn’t believe that. But I think someone who says something as absurd as that they’re going to… end lying, or whatever, is either taking the piss or mental.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I am not going to. I am not in such a position of power."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Oh, but if you were a despot, you could? Laughing my heart out, here. Your pure, beautiful soul.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "A... despot?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She sighs.* "What does that word mean?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “It’s like a worse monarch. Or one that didn’t bother to come up with a fancy title.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Ah."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Execution of all sinners could be accomplished with due time, no?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“No. God, I don’t even consider myself that politically informed, but how is this not obvious?”

Soul stops the car, and Hirer keeps talking. “Power is built on… well, power, that’s true. But it’s also built on successfully keeping up a con and dividing and conquering. The King is able to rob people blind by justifying it with fancy words and making them thing it’s only the natural thing, and when he can, doing it in small enough increments that it’s easy to ignore. If he said he was gonna kill everyone and backed up that claim believably? He’d basically be already a dead man.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “The ruled always outnumber the ruler.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Kill 'everyone'? You're exaggerating."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Who the fuck hasn’t sinned? I’ve seen cultists less deluded than you.”

“Get out the damn car.” Soul asks.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Sinning here only refers to lying."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She leaves the car.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Oh, okay. Replace what I said with lied, dumbass. I mean, did you grow up in a monastery, or something?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "No, but I prefer to believe in humanity."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Evidently, you do not. Sinner."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Yeah, alright. I’d love to watch your circus act from the sidelines.” He exits the car. “You have your weird jerkoff power fantasy over and over and once you’re the only one left, realize saying you wouldn’t kill everyone was a lie! Wonder if you’d stick to your principles then?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It would not have been a lie, merely a mistaken belief."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Your black-and-white views explain how you could believe 'everyone' has lied quite well."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Do you want me to beat the shit out of you? Hey, I’d have been nothing but honest in front of you if I did that.” 

Soul opens a hidden door in some warehouse exterior.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I would prefer you to change your mind."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “You’re ascribing too much sentimental intent to this. I never *wanted* to do it.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She groans.* "I *did* have a gun."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I don't care for your logic, sinner. Stop wasting my time."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Ok, dipshit. Lemme know when you realize the assholes who tell you straight to your face they’re fucking you are the worst ones.” He runs ahead to catch up to Soul.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "You are a lawyer. If anything, you have a vested interest in others believing that."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She runs ahead after him.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I do not inherently take exception to being fucked, anyway, only to being murdered or lied to."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "I typically prefer not to be physically harmed if it can be avoided. That is all."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
Hirer Dreng talks to the person with coherent beliefs instead. “Lady, I don’t know what exactly you want from me…”

“I don’t want anything from you. I’m just keeping as much in order as I can.” She leads the two down a corridor.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "He was talking to me."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She continues following.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Ok, cause I really ought to be getting out of… whatever this is. See, I got a family. Young kid, real heartbreaking stuff…”

“I don’t care and I didn’t ask.” 

“Right. Right, okay.” He slinks behind to the back of the pack.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I do not believe anything you did on Earth would move you significantly closer to finding this supposed family."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “That would be the idea, obviously. To send him back. But that’s not really an option.” Soul yawns.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “You had one too, right? That boy who transferred with you.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Ichigo Culbasko?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
“Sure, th—Culbasko?” She makes a very specific difficult to describe uncomfortable exhale.
“Whatever. He’s like that. A tagalong for whatever the new guys name was. Intelligence Override.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "What?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Man, I don’t know. IO. It was… Intuition! That was it, yeah. I would not have activated that sort of partner feature if it was my call. Clearly wasn’t tested. A version of the other person materializes in the other world… and that’s it. Isn’t ‘transferred’ in a proper sense.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Huh."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "It likely functions how it does out of necessity."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “No. I mean, that’s not how it works for you guys. You don’t have discontinuous existences in Earth and Arctica, or one confusing existence that overlaps.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Yes, but the rules of Arctica may be different in some way."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Earth is real, Arctica is not."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “That wouldn’t explain the discrepancy at all. Ichigo and…Hirer. One comes from Earth and the other Arctica. Both experience this erroneous progression. You and Horatius. From both of the two, but both don’t.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Ghrk."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "That reminds me. Hirer Dreng, do you know the name of the planet Arctica resides on?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
Hirer Dreng is no longer here.

Soul speaks up after the noticeable silence. “He can’t have gone far, and he won’t be able to leave this facility. I can track him easily later.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She snorts.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are we nearly at your lab?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: She reaches some room with a keypad, and presses a few buttons on it. ((I’m ending the fcuking session here I chose not to skip over all the travel and we all paid the price with hirer dreng characterization ))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content:
“…Significantly closer to it now. Rikarasu… do you know of Oppenheimer?”
She continues through the labyrinth of corridors.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I've... heard the name. Go on."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Yeah. Guy had a big role in the Manhattan project. Arguably more infamous for how much it destroyed him, the guilty conscience he carried and how it motivated his every action. But…”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Is he still alive?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “What? Nah, he died long before you were even born.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: “Anyway. Lot of people fucking hated him. Not even all for the reasons you’d expect.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Unsurprising. But how does this relate to anything today?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “It’s… I don’t know, I kind of thought you’d have more of an opinion. Is that racist? I guess it probably is.” She sighs. “Truman fuckin’ hated him. Called him a little crybaby shithead and that he didn’t even drop the bomb, I, Harry God Damn Truman, did. It’s a funny quote. The point is that nobody likes someone consumed by regret.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "How old are you?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
She laughs. “Older than I look. Much older.” She looks to be in her thirties.

The path she’s taking you finally leads out of the complex. This is Washington, DC.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are you friends with the President?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “No. Not at all. We’re enemies by proxy, I guess? The whole mess of politics is a lot to explain.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Is this not a risky place for you to be? The police would shoot you on sight."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “They have no idea what I look like.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "My point stands."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “No, it doesn’t. Why did you lie to that lawyer guy, by the way? Was it to piss him off? I can understand that, I guess.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Lie to him? How so?" *She seems slightly offended.* "I am not a sinner."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Well, that’s the biggest one. I can read the chat logs, you know. Obviously you don’t actually believe anyone who lies deserves death, unless you’re just incredibly bad at suicide.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "I am a detective who may operate under differing names in order to catch sinners. That's different."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “So lying is okay as long as you have a good reason?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...No. It's... I can choose and reject any name for myself. That isn't lying."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “What about insisting you know nothing about a PDA, about The Antarctica Project or anything? That also isn’t lying? Is the trick that you’re a detective?”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "When did I insist that?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Okay, you’ve reached the limit of my interest. It’s the part where I pull out chat receipts to argue obvious things with you. This is clearly your sticking point, and I’ll live with it when you seem otherwise rational.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Pah. I'm glad you at least recognise my intelligence otherwise. I am rational in every way.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are *you* behind the project?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “No. I’m related, though, yeah. Almost feels embarrassing to admit now. I’m like some hipster; oh, I was into TAP when it was cool, before they sold out to incompetent management!”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Did you just call it 'TAP'?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Yeah. The Antarctica Project. TAP. Acronym.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Who would abbreviate the name for a series of kidnappings?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “That isn’t what it is. Well, okay, yeah, it’s that. But not exclusively. The CIA is a kidnapping organization that does other things and they get an acronym. Fair’s fair.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "...Sure."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Anyway, how many people know about this?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Christ, way too many. I mean, it depends on what you even mean by ‘know’. Vigilante thugs are the ones who personally transported participants in the specific case that was needed, but they didn’t know shit about The Antarctica Project, it was just a job. And the history of this whole thing goes way back…”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "So... It's an ancient conspiracy, in the vein of the Illuminati. Is everyone in Arctica another victim just like us, then? Do they wish to form a new earth by forcing groups like us to adapt to the environment?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Ancient conspiracy is giving it too much credit. It’s barely even one cohesive mass now, let alone the fragments that would eventually lead to all this.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "How are you so sure?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “I know… a lot. Just… let me think for a bit, okay? I’ll explain once we’re finally at our destination.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: ((this is my excuse to end the session and then also skip next time to when the fucking thing actually happens))

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: She leads you, one way or another, into a small suburban house, just past the entrance of which is a stairway leading down. She looks back at you with an uncertain expression.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: *She looks forward at her.* "..."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "Are you okay?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “…Yeah. I’m fine. Just… feels weird to be at this point.” She heads downstairs.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "It feels weird to be in 'Washington, DC'. Exactly how did we arrive there from Japan by *walking*?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: *She follows.*

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: “Teleportation.” She answers this simple question.

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: "Teleportation is not real."

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content: "...Or do you admit this land is Arctica?"

author.name: pichuis
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\067a034b6637690fc6e7a1ce319ff6e2-B09A8.png

messages.content:
She snickers. “What do you know about what’s real?”

The basement… is a mess.

Wires trail every which way. There’s at least 1 square foot of monitor for every two square feet of wall, some still on, running something or another, others off. A large section of wall is left without any tech, and instead covered in papers, clippings, documents, all connected with pushpins and rubber bands and string. 

A circle of twelve images lies at the center of this wall. There are photographs of the five participants from Earth you recognize, and one more photograph you don’t. There are sketches of what look vaguely like Intuition Overdrive and the deceased George Tanaka, and four other sketches you do not recognize. These are simply the biggest images on the wall; there is much, much more information.

In the corner of the room is a sci-fi looking device akin to a freezer. In the center is a sci-fi looking device resembling a claw on the ceiling above an elevated platform on the floor.

“Sorry about the mess. This isn’t really for… anyone else.”

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png

messages.content: https://youtu.be/GQNKwJFuHQc

author.name: scipe
author.avatarUrl: C:\Users\Aidan\Documents\TAP Reading Order\json version\ASSETS forma de json\0a858383a5c98e5e573e49bf3f2bdbe1-9F159.png
